From nomic-business-owner@teleport.com Tue Jun 20 08:14:39 1995
Return-Path: nomic-business-owner@teleport.com
Received: from desiree.teleport.com (desiree.teleport.com [192.108.254.11]) by Shamino.quincy.edu (8.6.9/8.6.9) with ESMTP id IAA19745 for <blahedo@quincy.edu>; Tue, 20 Jun 1995 08:06:02 -0500
Received: (from daemon@localhost) by desiree.teleport.com (8.6.10/8.6.9) id GAA20299 for nomic-business-outgoing; Tue, 20 Jun 1995 06:05:32 -0700
Received: from Shamino.quincy.edu (blahedo@Shamino.quincy.edu [192.217.45.2]) by desiree.teleport.com (8.6.10/8.6.9) with ESMTP id GAA20287 for <nomic-business@teleport.com>; Tue, 20 Jun 1995 06:05:26 -0700
Received: (from blahedo@localhost) by Shamino.quincy.edu (8.6.9/8.6.9) id IAA19740 for nomic-business@teleport.com; Tue, 20 Jun 1995 08:05:41 -0500
From: Don Blaheta <blahedo@quincy.edu>
Message-Id: <199506201305.IAA19740@Shamino.quincy.edu>
Subject: BUS: Proto: Index/Proposal Consolidation and Reform
To: nomic-business@teleport.com (Agora Nomic)
Date: Tue, 20 Jun 1995 08:05:41 -0500 (CDT)
In-Reply-To: <199505271000.FAA13467@Shamino.quincy.edu> from "Don Blaheta" at May 27, 95 05:00:43 am
X-Mailer: ELM [version 2.4 PL23]
