Wow, the listserver has been unusually quiet lately...

Anyway, I have a brief announcement, and a request.

First, I'm working on a perl script to be a CGI script with which to
access the Archives.  So far, I've got it doing queries on the Voting
records, and my ultimate goal for the project is that everything will
tie together.

Now the request: What kinds of queries will you be wanting to make on
the Archives?  Here are the ones I've come up with so far:
List All Players
Voting Records for one Player
Voting on one Proposal
Text of one Proposal
Text of one Rule
Mailing address of one Player
Mailing address of all Players
Text of the Ruleset on a certain date

in no particular order; please mail me with any suggestions, no matter
how outrageous--I have a *lot* of information here, it just needs a bit
of organization.  (I mean, with logs of all listserver mail, I think I
can extract just about anything....)

