Subject: RE: Proposal "686.1"?
Sender: owner-nomic-discussion@teleport.com
Precedence: bulk
Reply-To: nomic-discussion@teleport.com
Status: RO

>Can someone please tell me why there is a Proposal which was numbered
>"686.1"??  It's giving me headaches all over the place trying to write
>scripts for the Archives...

That was due to the old "proposed Rule Change" language.  The
Rules specified that "proposed Rule Changes" were to receive
consecutive integers.  I was speaker at the time, and my interpretation
was that since this proposal was not a proposed Rule Change, it
should not receive the number 687 (which was reserved for the
next proposed Rule Change).

As to why you cannot find proposal 687, I do not know.  There
should be one.

Chuck

