> allow the Speaker to absorb all Ambassadorial duties.  since become
> Speaker over four weeks ago, the only official duty i have had to
> perform (aside from those of being a Justice) was to serve as
> temporary Notary for a couple of days.  however, if Ian doesn't get
> off his can and announce Coren's deregistration soon i shall have to
> step in there and do it for him. :)

If the Internomic thing goes through, I'd imagine the Ambassador would
have plenty to do--and besides, the post of Ambassador should be a
little more stable than that of Speaker currently is.

