>
>"Steve" == Steve Gardner <gardner@aurora.cc.monash.edu.au> writes:
>
>Steve> Not so fast, Swann! The reasons why I regard Michael's cron
>Steve> script as a legal way for him to vote are entirely to do with
>Steve> the specific way in which Rule 683 is worded: it says that "in
>Steve> order to be legally cast, a vote by a Player or a Group must be
