Reply to message from chess@watson.ibm.com of Fri, 11 Aug
>
>Wait!  You're saying that there are Agora Players who are
>not in Recursa, and *vice-versa*??   The membership of
>Recursa (a Contest within Agora) is -not- a subset of the
