Well, in theroy its simple, Recursa having jurisdiction over its own
voting, proposals, etc.  The fuzzy bits only come in at the 
Agora/Recursa interface.  (Theoretically it is currently possible for
a Contestant in Recursa cease to be a Contestant (a legal Agora distinction)
