Received: (from daemon@localhost) by desiree.teleport.com (8.6.10/8.6.9) id WAA26311 for nomic-discussion-outgoing; Sun, 13 Aug 1995 22:27:36 -0700
Received: from aurora.cc.monash.edu.au (gardner@aurora.cc.monash.edu.au [130.194.1.91]) by desiree.teleport.com (8.6.10/8.6.9) with ESMTP id WAA26298 for <nomic-discussion@teleport.com>; Sun, 13 Aug 1995 22:27:32 -0700
Received: (gardner@localhost) by aurora.cc.monash.edu.au (8.6.12/8.6.4) id PAA19993 for nomic-discussion@teleport.com; Mon, 14 Aug 1995 15:27:05 +1000
From: Steve Gardner <gardner@aurora.cc.monash.edu.au>
