This morning, I got email from one Dariush Gholizadeh, wondering if
Agora Nomic would be interested in a business partnership.  I clarified
the nature of Agora (an informal but international association of
people) for him, and he responded with a more clear description of what
he was working on.  Here, then, is his response and my response to it.
(He requested that this be forwarded to you-all.)  In response to my
question about the staff, he stated that young actors will be paid by
his company for the recordings.

