H. Promotor, take note!  This was Proto'd Thu, 2 Nov 95 16:55:01 EST.

Proposal ____, AI=1, proto'd
Recognize Canada

   The present Directive on Foreign Policy Business of the Agora
   Nomic recognizes the nation of Canada as a peer Nomic. The Ambassador
   of Agora is hereby instructed to present official Greetings from the
   Players of Agora to the Citizens of Canada, along with a copy of this
   Directive.

(By popular demand!  Thanks to Morendil for the underlying wording.
 I'm not sure whether to say "Citizens" or "Government" here, since
 the silly Canadians have separated the two; I guess that's what
 happens when you get too many Players.  "Citizens" seems more
 egalitarian and Agora-ish.  The required presentation of Greetings
 could be done, for instance, by a posting to some general
 Canadian newsgroup...)

