But we need the Number of the Proposal to Repeal each Rule, so we'll
need the text of each Proposal. After all, there are many Rules which
really should be Repealed; we would encourage everyone to compare the
current Rules on the Public Forum to the Distributor Rules; we could
make some CFJ's and probably throw the whole system into chaos. 

We would encourage everyone to actually examine at least some of the
Rules determine if they really serve a purpose in the current Game. Many
of them can and should be Repealed. And again, anyone making blanket
Votes either FOR or AGAINST the Green Repeals will be held in contempt.


