From my list of Stare Decisis:
Rule 478:
CFJ 752 (Judged by Swann, upheld upon appeal by CotC):

Something sent to someone in such a way that that person has the obligation
to send it to all Players is sufficient for it having been sent to the
Public Forum.

(this is my own transcription of the part of the Judgement which is of more
than singular importance).

Now I'm talking about the Stare Decisis-list anyway:

Would the Archivist please forward to me the text (including the Arguments
of the Judges & Justices) of all CFJs from 760 onwards?

