Sure it is!  A Proposal can contain zero of each.  Remember
Agoran Friendly Thoughts Day?

  PROPOSAL 1701 (Favor) AI=1, protoed
  Friendly-Thoughts Day

  This Proposal contains no Rules Changes and no Directives.

  WHEREAS the growth and well-being of Agora Nomic depends
  critically upon the civility and mutual good-will of its
  Players,

  THEREFORE be it resolved that Friday, September 1, 1995
  shall be an Agoran Friendly Thoughts Day, upon which all
  Agorans may consider the good aspects of their fellow
  Players, and try to find something to admire in even the
  most tenuous scam, the silliest Judgement, and the longest
  thread about the meanings of common words.

See the first sentence of 1483.  It's *very* definite...

