Proto-Proposal
---
Proposal Codes

Amend Rule 109 by replacing the text :

   The Promotor shall give each submitted Proposal a Number for 
   reference.

with

   Each submitted Proposal shall be assigned a Proposal ID,
   in the form of a four-letter Proposal Code uniquely identifying
   the Player submitting that Proposal, to which a Proposal Number 
   shall be appended.

and replacing

   to a Proposal

with

   to a Proposal with the same Proposal Code

and appending the paragraph :

   The Promotor is responsible for assigning Proposal Codes, unless
   otherwise specified in other Rules.
---

Comments : paves the way for a Player Promoting eir own
Proposals.

Revision history :

1 - 10 Nov., original proto

