Let's see...there are Theses, which are admittedly rather
limited. Just brainstorming:

Action to be rewarded:
Getting more Players
Improving cultural life of Agora
Acquiring RL resources (computer space, programs, et. al.)
Clever ideas for Contests
Finding loopholes in Rules
Creating paradox
Gaining recognition from outside sources

Possible Rewards:
Freedom from obeying certain, limited Rules 
Preferential Judgeship
Ability to mint own currency
Ownership of Virtual Real-estate
Ability to expedite certain Proposals or CFJ's

(note most of the above I would term "unfair" unless
limited in duration)

