Ambassador Shall Prevent Abuse of Agora Mailing Lists

The following Foreign Policy Directive is hereby adopted:

      The Ambassador is directed to detect unwanted and improper usage of
      recognized Agora mailing lists by entities which are not involved in the
      Game. E shall pursue methods generally considered acceptable for dealing
