Proto-Proposal
Don't spam the server
(Amends a rule)

Whereas Foreign Policy Directives do not change often, and

Whereas some Foreign Policy Directives are extremely long,

Be it therefore resolved that Rule 1070 be amended by changing the
paragraph that currently reads

      The Ambassador shall maintain a record of all Foreign Policy
      Directives.  The Ambassador shall publish active FPD's at least
      once per Nomic Game Week.

to read as follows:

      The Ambassador shall maintain a record of all Foreign Policy
      Directives, and shall make that record available to all Players.

first proto: 23 Oct 1995
second proto: 16 Nov 1995

