Protoproposal Birthday-1

Let the following Rule be created:

Birthdays

  A Player may inform the Registrar of his or her Birthday.
If they do so, then on that day they may select and receive
ONE (1) of the following 'presents':
   Three EV's
   Two Win Tokens created and given to them
   Two Blots erased (as long as neither Blot is the
recipient's last Blot)
   One Kudo created and given to them
   The ability to submit up to 20 Proposals on that
day without penalty
   
In addition, all Players are hereby encouraged to
wish the recipient a Happy Birthday.
  This Rule takes precedence over any Rule preventing
the recipient from receiving any of the above presents.

[FYI, my birthday is Nov. 23, so I will probably be the
last Player to derive any advantage from this Rule]

--------------------------------------
   
Protoproposal Travel-1

Let the Following Rule be created:

Greetings from Overseas!

Any time a Player travels to a foreign country,
he/she shall announce that fact in the Public Forum
at least one week before he/she departs (if possible).
Any other Player may then request the traveller to
send him/her a postcard from the destination country,
as long as the Player does so before the traveller
departs. The traveller is then obligated to do so,
provided the Player requesting a postcard provides
his/her address.
  For the purposes of this Rule, "travel to a foreign
country" can include intermediate destinations
if applicable, but does not include any destination which
lies in the traveller's native country, country of
residence, or any nation in which the traveller spends 
less than 48 contiguous hours.
 Violation of this Rule is a Class D Crime.

[Note, as a Classical Archaeologist, this Rule will
apply to me as much as anyone.]
------------------------------------------------

Vlad

