Agorans wishing to include the full and correct text of any Rule can
now use the Nomic macro preprocessor ! This new service is hosted
by cdrompro.com.

To use, send your Judgement, Official Report or whatever to one of:
  preproc-discussion@cdrompro.com
  preproc-business@cdrompro.com
  preproc-official@cdrompro.com
and include within a macro of the form
  <RXXXX>
where XXXX is the number of a Rule.

Your mail will be bounced to the appropriate Agora list, with macros 
expanded to full Rules.

I'll welcome any suggestions on how 'preproc' can be developed into 
an even more useful service to the Agoran community. Please remember 
that 'preproc' is just out of testing and there may still be some 
kinks that I haven't ironed out yet.

-*-*-*-*-*-
 Morendil

