Subject: Status of Win Bookie Contest
Sender: owner-nomic-discussion@teleport.com
Precedence: bulk
Reply-To: nomic-discussion@teleport.com
Status: RO

Now that kelly's re-registered, I have a puzzle: kelly was the
only Contestant in the Contest at the time e deregistered last
game.  E had contributed 5 Marks to the Treasury, and there was
a Bet in existence associated with em.  What's the status now?
The Contest still exists: is kelly a Contestant?  If not, is
the Bet still associated with em?  Is there a clear answer to
this, or does it need a CFJ?  I'll attach the Regs.

| favor |

CONTEST: The Win Bookie

Regulations:

1. The Entry Fee for this Contest shall be 5 Marks.

2. At any time after joining the Contest, each Contestant may
   send the Contestmaster a Bet Application, marked as such and
   naming a Player who is the Target for that Bet Application.
   For each Bet Application beyond the first that a given
   Contestant sends to the Contestmaster, that Contestant
   must transfer an additional 5 Marks to the Contest Treasury.

3. Exactly one week after a Bet Application is sent to the
   Contestmaster, it becomes a Bet.  The Target of a Bet is
   the same as the Target of the corresponding Bet Application,
   and the Owner of a Bet is the Contestant who sent the
   Bet Application.

3. When a Player Wins a Game of Agora Nomic, the following shall occur:
   * If any Contestant is the Owner of a Bet whose Target is the
     winning Player, half the treasury is divided among the Contestants,
     weighted linearly according to the number of Bets each
     Contestant Owns with the winning Player as Target.
   * Every Contestant must transfer 1 Mark to the Contest Treasury
     for each Bet of eirs that is still in effect.

4. A Contestant may leave the Contest at any time by sending a message
   to the Contestmaster notifying em.  When a Contestant does this,
   all Bet Applications sent by that Contestant, and all Bets Owned
   by that Contestant, cease to exist.

5. The Contestmaster may transfer the Contestmastership to any
   consenting Player of Agora Nomic.

6. The Contestmaster shall send a list of all current Bets and
   Bet Applications to any Contestant upon request.

7. The regulations may be changed at any time by unanimous agreement
   of the Contestants, and the consent of the Contestmaster.

Contestmaster favor

