Steve is attempting to put words in my mouth that I can not and do not agree
with.  I maintain that two crimes are committed when D2 occurs; the crime of
performing D2 before D0 and the crime of performing D2 before D1.  The
remainder of Steve's argument is now irrelevant, since it is based on premises
which are invalid.  

