Also, re: pranks and stuff: Coren and I have been talking, and I meant
to post this earlier:

There are two flags we can raise on the Agora servers, one which
prevents anyone from subscribing without approval, and another which
prevents any unsubscribed person from sending mail to the lists.

*I* think that we should implement the second but not the first,
although Coren rightly points out that setting both flags would make the
recent sort of spam impossible.  Opinions?

