Subject: Re: BUS: PROTO:Agoraspace v2.2
To: nomic-discussion@teleport.com
Date: Wed, 29 Nov 1995 17:46:14 -0600 (CST)
In-Reply-To: <199511291424.JAA06037@piglet.INS.CWRU.Edu> from "Steven A Swiniarski" at Nov 29, 95 09:24:25 am
X-Mailer: ELM [version 2.4 PL24]
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=US-ASCII
