        Steve writes,
     
        "WHat seems unclear to you in Rule 869? Is it uncertainty      
        about how to send to the Public Forum?"
     
     
     No, I had no problem finding the address to the Public Forum.  
     What I did find unclear was the following part of Rule 869:
     
     "Registration occurs when a person who is not a Player sends a 
     message to the Public Forum requesting to be Registered."
     
     I interpreted this sentence to say that, since I was requesting 
     to be registered, someone (or something) would accept or reject 
     my request.  I think the following would be more clear:
     
     "Registration occurs when a person who is not a Player sends a 
     message to the Public Forum stating that Player's intent to be 
     Registered."
     
     Marc.

