Proto-Proposal
---
Shorten Voting Period

Amend Rule 693 by replacing the words 'ten days' with 'one week'.
---

Comments: the Week seems to be the basic unit of Agora business,
and the one we're most comfortable with. Shortening the Voting
Period conforms with this Custom, and Players will no be less 
deterred from Proposing significant reforms one Rule at a time 
instead of in large chunks of Rule Changes.

