From nomic-business-owner@teleport.com  Thu Dec 14 02:43:14 1995
Received: from desiree.teleport.com (desiree.teleport.com [192.108.254.21]) by Shamino.quincy.edu (8.6.12/8.6.9) with ESMTP id CAA13577 for <blahedo@quincy.edu>; Thu, 14 Dec 1995 02:43:12 -0600
