Subject: BUS: Official Judgement: Appeal of CFJ 835
To: csg419@wing.rug.nl (Andre Engels)
Date: Thu, 14 Dec 1995 19:41:17 +1100 (EST)
Cc: nomic-business@teleport.com (Nomic Mailing List)
X-Mailer: ELM [version 2.4 PL21]
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=US-ASCII
