Proto-Proposal
---
Benefactors

Create a Rule with this text (Benefactors) :

   There exists a Patent Title of Benefactor, which is automatically 
   awarded to any Player who posts a set of Proposals such that, 
   first, each Proposal has as its effect if adopted the Repeal of 
   exactly one Rule; second, that each Rule in the Ruleset is 
   mentioned in one of these Proposals; third, that all these 
   Proposals are submitted in the same Nomic Week.

   This Rule respawns itself on a Repeal.
---

Comments : Chromatic Repeals are a Good Thing or a Bad Thing, 
depending on one's point of view; this has the advantage of correctly 
reflecting both opinions, in establishing a Title which is either a 
form of praise or heavy irony, depending on which side you're on. :)

Revision history :
1 - Dec. 15, original proto

